<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[أَضِمَ]</span> عليه أَضَماً: إِذا غضب.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
